title: No. 7 Duke Outlasts Virginia Tech, 15-14 - Duke University - GoDuke.com
content: No. 7 Duke Outlasts Virginia Tech, 15-14 - Duke University  GoDuke.com
description: BLACKSBURG, Va. - The seventh-ranked Duke women's lacrosse team captured a 15-14 victory on the road against Virginia Tech Thursday evening in Blacksburg, Va.
